OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLow cloud
OL,6,Fmaking its way back inland to affect
OL,7,Fmany places during the evening and
OL,8,Fovernight, staying dry for most with a
OL,9,Flight northeasterly breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FA cloudy morning but quickly
OL,12,Fbecoming a bright and sunny day for
OL,13,Fmany. Low cloud lingers along the
OL,14,Fcoast where it remains cooler in a
OL,15,Flight northeasterly wind.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
