OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMorning
OL,6,Fcloud retreating to coasts on Friday.
OL,7,FA slightly cloudier feel to Saturday
OL,8,Fbut staying dry. Bright and sunny for
OL,9,Fmost on Sunday. Temperatures around or
OL,10,Fslightly above average.
